title: Target lays off 235 in Twin Cities tech operations
text: Target lays off 235 in Twin Cities tech operations Tuesday, 1 September 2015 (14 minutes ago) Retailer Target Corp. has laid off about 235 employees in its technology operations in the Twin Cities. Target laid off another 235 headquarters employees on Tuesday.
